Package: Mona
Title: Single Cell RNA Visualization/Exploration
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given="Konrad",family="Thorner",email="Konrad.Thorner@cchmc.org",role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny app for analyzing single cell data, designed to allow for fast and easy visualization after processing with Seurat or similar tools. The key feature is the flexible plotting interface, where users can create multiple interactive plots of multiple types at once. Other functions include the ability to subset/annotate cells, calculate markers, find associated GO terms, and transfer labels between datasets. 
License: `use_mit_license()`
